p.d: Looking for more detailed information about martial arts? This documentary style program gives you the inside scoop on what it takes to be a champion in any number of disciplines. In this edition of “Beyond MMA” Mixed Martial Arts is examined more closely. Learn how this sport has evolved and where the roots of the world’s most popular fighting sport come from.
